gold.dim+products
*Puropose - Provides inforamtion about products and their attributes
*Columns

Column Name                 |Data Type      |     Description
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
product_key                 |INT            |Surrogate key uniquely identyfing each product record in the product dimension table
product_id                  |INT            |A unique identyfier assigned to the product for internal tracking and referencing
product_number              |NVARCHAR(50)   |A structured code representing product, often used for categorization inventory 
